  "description": "Update Contact Card Visual Design and Alignment\n\nRedesign the contact card component to improve its visual appearance and ensure it matches the design system used throughout the rest of the page.\n\nRequirements:\n- Review the current page design to identify consistent visual patterns (spacing, colors, typography, borders, shadows)\n- Update contact card styling to match the established design language\n- Ensure proper alignment with surrounding page elements\n- Improve visual hierarchy within the card (name, title, contact info, etc.)\n- Apply consistent padding and margins to align with page grid system\n- Update typography to match page font sizes, weights, and styles\n- Adjust colors, borders, and shadows to be cohesive with overall page theme\n- Ensure card is responsive and maintains visual consistency across different screen sizes\n- Verify adequate contrast ratios for accessibility\n- Test visual appearance in context of the full page layout",
